  "title": "Despatch Cum Warehouse Assistant (Kallang)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Manage and maintain warehouse operations and inventory levels.</li>\n  <li>Pick and pack implant sets based on sales team orders.</li>\n  <li>Deliver implants and instrument sets to hospitals in a timely manner.</li>\n  <li>Inspect incoming shipments and organize materials within the warehouse.</li>\n  <li>Issue purchase orders and verify accuracy of all accompanying documentation.</li>\n  <li>Monitor stock levels and check product expiry dates to ensure quality compliance.</li>\n  <li>Participate in annual stock counts and inventory audits.</li>\n  <li>Assist the Admin Manager with administrative tasks and other ad-hoc duties as required.</li>\n  <li>Utilize the ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning) system for efficient warehouse and inventory management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a Class 3 Driving License is preferred.</li>\n  <li>Preferable basic knowledge in Microsoft Office and ERP</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981| EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
